        },
        "subject": "LU-19161 lnet: Handle timeout correctly in lnd_nl_set",
        "message": "LU-19161 lnet: Handle timeout correctly in lnd_nl_set\n\nThe lnd_timeout in the lnd tunable structs is meant to report to\nuser-space the value of the LND timeout. However, this field is\nnot read by the LNDs to get their timeout, so writing to this via\nlnd_nl_set currently has no affect. Modify the lnd_nl_set methods to\nupdate their actual LND timeout.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I729018deca00bcfefe164cf62250a80b04372f99\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
